{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Embrace art of the Alchemy!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is a <strong>classic puzzle in the &quot;alchemy&quot; genre!</strong> At the beginning, you have <strong>only four basic elements,</strong> but over time <strong>your mastery will grow,</strong> and you will gain access to more <strong>complex recipes!</strong> An exciting adventure awaits you in the world of alchemical combinations! <strong>Discover over 1000 different elements!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/1.gif?t=1737762145\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unique setting</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The game</strong> takes place in a <i><strong>fantasy post-apocalyptic world</strong></i> on the brink of extinction due <strong>to a global cataclysm.</strong> With each completed quest, <strong>you will discover new corners</strong> of this world that can <strong>tell a story about its past.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/3.gif?t=1737762145\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Meet the local inhabitants</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>On your path to learning alchemy,</strong> you will meet <strong>fabulous creatures: elves, dragons, dwarves, Valkyries... spiders?!</strong> Each of them has its own story, which you can learn if you are <strong>curious enough!</strong> Chat with the <strong>characters to learn more</strong> about the incredible <strong>world of Fusion!</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549700/extras/2.gif?t=1737762145\" /><strong>Gameplay Features</strong></h2><ul cl